## [1.3] - 2016-08-11
- Upgrade to waf 1.9.9
- Workaround Sun CC 12.3 bug for using relative include paths

## [1.2] - 2016-08-11
- Upgrade to waf 1.9.2.
- Add Visual Studio 2015 to the list of compilers supported by bde_setwafenv.py.
- Bug fixes.

## [1.1] - 2016-02-23
- Always install headers of third-party packages into a subdirectory of
  includedir.
- Fixed SUN stlport build issue where "-library=stlport4" was misinterpreted as
  a library name.

## [1.0] - 2016-02-19
- Added versioning support -- wscript in project repos now can specify
  `min_bde_tools_version` and `max_bde_tools_version`
